title: Rob Moran from Unbroken/Narrows
itunes:title: Rob Moran from Unbroken/Narrows
description:
In this episode we interview Rob Moran (Unbroken, Narrows, Some Girls, Over My Dead Body), review new music from Bright Eyes, Rot In Hell and TIm Hecker. We also review the movie Cedar Rapids. Hilarity ensues.
